{"tid":1863072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本直送藥妝達人 食人肉饅頭","createTime":"2020-02-05T03:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T07:56:21.000Z","uid":259116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fd8346d88e4b24f13e2ad85b44d19eba3aa4f2","tid":1863072,"uid":259116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"見到好多人比呢間fb shop呃 有冇人都中左伏<br />\n有冇咩方法可以舉報佢 勁仆街 成個fb page冇左 <br />\n做香港人真慘 想買個口罩都要俾啲咁嘅仆街呃錢<br />\n推到佢仆街 俾返錢苦主 我估人數應該都多 <br />\n最後提醒大家 上網買口罩要小心<br />\n特別係啲近期先開嘅shop 保持警覺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gH0newN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgH0newN.jpg&h=d2b0e93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n由於太多查詢所以其他問題我哋唔會回覆，請包容，請落單需要兩盒係成人定小童。<br />\n<br />\n&bull;大人及小童$50一盒<br />\n&bull;日本白象牌醫療級口罩<br />\n由於存貨有限，所以大家只能每位限購(兩盒)，肺炎橫行，各位必須做足防禦措施。<br />\n<br />\n第一批口罩型號日本白象牌-即棄外科口罩(成人及小童)<br />\n小童 : 15.5cm x 8cm<br />\n成人 : 16.5cm x 9cm<br />\n小童及成人盒裝，50個/盒，三層高效能過濾。<br />\n▪細菌過濾 : 99.9%<br />\n▪粒子過濾 : 99.9%<br />\n▪病篤過濾 : 99.9%<br />\n適合面部線條，兩側加工。 <br />\n因為是3D加工，所以不會壓迫鼻子和嘴巴。<br />\n<br />\n中國銀行<br />\n012-748-2-006500-5<br />\nLee Ka Chai<br />\n(入數後請WhatsApp 61965633  收據核對)<br />\n<br />\n第一批貨2月5日到港，貨到會通知安排貨運。<br />\n<br />\n(麻煩先入數 然後安排送貨）<br />\n（只有中銀 請不要再問有沒有其他戶口）<br />\n(可bank in 或 網上理財過數，沒有轉數快/Payme)<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n口罩訂購先入數後送貨 , 因為太多人詢問 , 請耐心等候真人回覆❤<br />\n2月5日前 第一批入數的朋友保證可安排2⃣盒, 請直接發送入數單據 , 同事會盡快跟進‼️<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n剛剛盤點完畢🧮每人限購兩盒📌<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n如果入咗數🙏🏻<br />\n2月5日會安排送貨<br />\n順豐速遞 貨到付款<br />\n到時候才會要你提供送貨順豐地址"},{"pid":"654112bfa93ec97856a21187b6e5d938f8e89ff9","tid":1863072,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"私人戶口做生意？"},{"pid":"9d8706a7b2f35a04c92f35cfea4faeeb2b0d92d7","tid":1863072,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:39:29.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭，變咗 人肉饅頭？"},{"pid":"529d7b2e37841d02fc304fcfc48541fc09bd7572","tid":1863072,"uid":259116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8706a7b2f35a04c92f35cfea4faeeb2b0d92d7","tid":1863072,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:39:29.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭，變咗 人肉饅頭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔小心打錯左sorry"},{"pid":"36bce0e54063a32c45918e3517470c8d2777b4ad","tid":1863072,"uid":32850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"我都比佢呃左<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"0d9d81302ef4820dab4c0946036e2d9506261504","tid":1863072,"uid":259116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36bce0e54063a32c45918e3517470c8d2777b4ad","tid":1863072,"uid":32850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"我都比佢呃左<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"我fd去中銀舉報佢ac 話有機會退款 但要20工作天 你可以試下！"},{"pid":"65273ecbedd2aceb38bbee9ffc53a43b604904e4","tid":1863072,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9d81302ef4820dab4c0946036e2d9506261504","tid":1863072,"uid":259116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36bce0e54063a32c45918e3517470c8d2777b4ad","tid":1863072,"uid":32850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"我都比佢呃左<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"我fd去中銀舉報佢ac 話有機會退款 但要20工作天 你可以試下！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"係打電話去舉報?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697e456306a7e82d2c462d1354084